---
title: Southwestern-Style Pork Fajitas with Tomato Lime Salsa and Cheddar Cheese
description: So easy, fast and packed with flavour. Simple should be the middle name of this dish. Sweet peppers and onions pair perfectly with tender pork for a fun fajita meal that all comes together with our fabulous, Southwestern spice blend!
